==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mooncalf
<hw>Moon"calf`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
monster; a false conception; a mass of fleshy matter, generated in the
uterus.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A dolt; a stupid fellow.</def>
<rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Moon-culminating</ent>⟦br⟧
